dct_title_s: Map of part of Arabia showing the route of Lieut. Col. Pelly
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Col. Pelly's route colored red. Dates and locations of encampment are shown. From: The Journal of the Royal Geographical Society of London. Vol. 35, (1865), pp. 169-91; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J687 v.35 1865 "The position of places are inserted as laid down by Col. Pelly."
dct_publisher_sm: London : published for the Journal of the Royal Geographical Society by J. Murray, Albemarle Street, 1865.
